snippet.title: ORDER 13 | Official Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Cybernetic Walrus and Oro Interactive are excited to announce the launch date of their highly anticipated horror simulation game, ORDER 13, arriving on Steam March 10th, 2025

Since its reveal in January, ORDER 13 has accumulated over 4 million views across video platforms in the past month, with significant interest coming from IGN, Game Rant, and creators like Kingwoolz, and Insym driving its popularity.

What begins as a routine shift in a fulfillment center quickly turns into an unsettling experience. Players must navigate the warehouse, handle orders, and face disturbing encounters while uncovering the dark secrets lurking inside.

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2259310/ORDER_13/
